{
  "texts": [
    "• Recall (R): The proportion of correctly predicted positive aspects among all true positive aspects.",
    "where T P is the number of trule positives and F N is the number of false negatives.",
    "• F1-score (F1): The harmonic mean of precision and recall.",
    "• Accuracy (Acc): The proportion of correctly predicted aspects among all aspects.",
    "where T P is the number of true positives, T N is the number of true negatives, F P is the number of false positives, and F N is the number of false negatives."
  ]
}